snippet: San Francisco police say they have found dozens of meatballs suspected to be poisonous in a Twin Peaks neighborhood where a similar incident happened last year....

headline.print_headline: Police: Meatballs Left for Dogs May Be Poisonous
headline.main: Police: Meatballs Left for Dogs May Be Poisonous

lead_paragraph: San Francisco police say they have found dozens of meatballs suspected to be poisonous in a Twin Peaks neighborhood where a similar incident happened last year.
